  "description": "A driftwood log lies on a gray sand beach among gray rocks. The log is bleached white and appears weathered, with twisted branches extending from its main body. The beach is composed of dark, fine-grained sand, and is littered with numerous gray and dark rocks of varying sizes. Behind the beach and rocks, a hillside covered in green vegetation rises, including grasses and low-lying plants. The sky is bright and clear, indicating a sunny day. The scene evokes a sense of natural beauty and tranquility.",
